meta.title: C++ Class
meta.description: Creates a C++ header and a source file  for a new class that you can add to a C++ project.

meta.title: QML File
meta.description: Creates a QML file with boilerplate code,  starting with "import QtQuick".

meta.title: Qt Translation File
meta.description: Creates a translation file that you can add to a Qt project.

meta.title: Qt Widgets UI Designer Form
meta.description: Creates a Qt Widgets Designer form  that you can add to a Qt Widget Project. This is useful if you already have an existing class for the UI business logic.
